Confess. Admit your mistake.

344
00:29:18,690 --> 00:29:19,679
No.

345
00:29:25,964 --> 00:29:27,124
Very well.

346
00:29:29,835 --> 00:29:30,995
Dou Chou.

347
00:29:36,708 --> 00:29:37,868
No!

348
