You are responsible.

349
00:29:56,361 --> 00:29:58,420
Come on, Franklin.
Here. I'll help you.

350
00:32:00,018 --> 00:32:02,612
Let me get that one.
You get the small ones.

351
00:32:02,654 --> 00:32:04,747
