Stop him!

357
00:33:43,355 --> 00:33:44,583
What the hell?

358
00:33:57,002 --> 00:34:00,130
I hope I didn't scare you guys.

359
00:34:00,172 --> 00:34:01,935
How do you like
my new helicopter?

360
00:34:03,342 --> 00:34:04,741
You are a day early.

361
00:34:04,776 --> 00:34:08,337
I had to borrow it.
The other was too small.

362
00:34:08,380 --> 00:34:10,974
I've brought you an arsenal
that will discourage anyone...

363
00:34:11,016 --> 00:34:13,007
from cutting into
our opium business.

364
00:34:13,051 --> 00:34:17,852
Now all that can harm us are
your American friends.

365
00:34:17,889 --> 00:34:19,686
Why are they still alive?

366
00:34:19,725 --> 00:34:23,525
Francois, I have
the situation under control.

367
00:34:26,298 --> 00:34:28,129
Thanks for our treat.

368
00:34:28,166 --> 00:34:30,726
You're a hot little devil.

369
00:34:30,769 --> 00:34:33,795
You know, this time
they're all virgins.

370
00:34:36,074 --> 00:34:37,234
Come on, girls.

371
