we can do about it now.

373
00:34:47,319 --> 00:34:49,844
At least we know what they're
putting in that hut.

374
00:34:49,888 --> 00:34:51,116
Those boxes?

375
00:34:51,156 --> 00:34:53,386
They're full of weapons.

376
00:34:53,425 --> 00:34:55,188
That's our way out.

377
00:34:56,528 --> 00:34:58,792
When do you aim to kill
the Americans?

378
00:34:58,830 --> 00:35:00,593
In my own time.

379
00:35:00,632 --> 00:35:02,759
You're risking
our entire operation...

380
00:35:02,801 --> 00:35:04,291
a very profitable operation.

381
00:35:04,336 --> 00:35:06,429
I'm thinking of
getting a new watch.

382
00:35:06,471 --> 00:35:09,338
Do you think you can purchase
one of those digital models?

383
00:35:11,176 --> 00:35:14,168
I told you to kill
the Americans, goddamn it!

384
00:35:14,212 --> 00:35:17,147
If the P.O.W. Search team hears
about it, we're finished!

385
00:35:17,182 --> 00:35:19,275
Don't let your stupid ego
ruin everything!

386
00:35:26,591 --> 00:35:29,424
Francois, will you
come with me for a moment?

387
00:35:34,966 --> 00:35:36,695
Look, I didn't want to...

388
00:35:38,303 --> 00:35:42,899
You will never again speak to me
like that in front of my men.

389
00:35:42,941 --> 00:35:44,738
It sets a dangerous example.

390
00:35:47,145 --> 00:35:48,635
Do you understand me?

391
00:35:51,316 --> 00:35:52,578
Good.

392
00:35:55,153 --> 00:36:01,422
Do you have any new information
about the American search team?

393
00:36:01,460 --> 00:36:04,395
No. It's still rumors...

394
00:36:04,429 --> 00:36:08,297
but there's been a guy
hanging around asking questions.

395
00:36:12,604 --> 00:36:13,969
I wonder if Opelka is dead.

396
00:36:14,005 --> 00:36:17,031
No. If he were...

397
00:36:17,075 --> 00:36:19,737
Colonel Yin would stick his body
right in front of our faces.

398
00:36:23,748 --> 00:36:26,842
So, my friend,
could I convince you...

399
00:36:26,885 --> 00:36:29,445
to spend the night
with us and the virgins?

400
00:36:30,789 --> 00:36:32,757
Sorry. I better not.

401
00:36:32,791 --> 00:36:33,917
Understand...

402
00:36:33,959 --> 00:36:35,756
I'm delivering
the opium personally...

403
00:36:35,794 --> 00:36:38,024
but I will be back
to pick up the girls.

404
00:36:42,167 --> 00:36:43,464
Don't forget my watch.

405
00:37:12,497 --> 00:37:17,434
Colonel Braddock, Francois
brought me something today...

406
00:37:17,469 --> 00:37:19,664
that I'm sure is of
great interest to you.

407
00:37:21,907 --> 00:37:27,368
It seems your ex-wife has
finally written you a letter.

408
00:37:39,257 --> 00:37:42,784
Unfortunately,
you must be punished...

409
00:37:42,827 --> 00:37:46,888
for the incident with
your late friend... Opelka.

410
00:37:46,932 --> 00:37:47,921
