473
00:43:22,667 --> 00:43:24,532
How large is your rescue team?

474
00:43:24,569 --> 00:43:26,059
Large enough to kick
Yin's ass, huh?

475
00:43:29,574 --> 00:43:30,563
I'm alone.

476
00:43:35,046 --> 00:43:36,377
Alone?

477
00:43:36,414 --> 00:43:38,109
Nobody knows I'm here, mate.

478
00:43:39,817 --> 00:43:42,012
Man, there's nobody
gonna come and get me.

479
00:43:42,053 --> 00:43:44,283
But the International
Freedom House...

480
00:43:44,322 --> 00:43:46,153
The Central Team,
The homing device?

481
00:43:46,190 --> 00:43:48,317
It's just a bluff, isn't it?
I had to tell him something.

482
00:43:48,359 --> 00:43:49,917
I've heard rumors
about this place.

483
00:43:49,961 --> 00:43:51,223
I followed Francois in.

484
00:43:51,262 --> 00:43:52,820
