photographer, mate.

485
00:43:52,864 --> 00:43:55,162
I needed pictures for proof.

486
00:43:55,199 --> 00:43:56,325
Damn!

487
00:43:56,367 --> 00:43:59,859
One thing for sure,
he's got guts.

488
00:43:59,904 --> 00:44:05,274
Yeah. Nobody ever broke
into a prison camp.

489
00:44:05,310 --> 00:44:08,143
All right, then, let's get out.
We'll head for the cliffs.

490
00:44:08,179 --> 00:44:09,305
Anything happens to me...

491
00:44:09,347 --> 00:44:10,575
