Head for the Thai border...

493
00:44:11,916 --> 00:44:13,281
100 miles due west.
Come on, let's go.

494
00:44:13,318 --> 00:44:16,651
Wait. Yin may let you go...

495
00:44:16,688 --> 00:44:18,952
but he certainly
won't let us all go.

496
00:44:18,990 --> 00:44:20,218
What's that?

497
00:44:20,258 --> 00:44:23,352
